%p.article-title Great news!
%p.article-content= "#{@provider.first_name} has indicated they are available to look after #{@owner.pet_name} on #{@enquiry.date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)}!"
- if @enquiry.response_message.present?
  %p.article-content= "#{@provider.first_name} has also included the following message:"
  %p.article-content
    %strong= @enquiry.response_message
%p.article-title What happens next
%p.article-content= "Contact #{@provider.first_name} to work out any additional details you want to know. Make sure you are fully confident of leaving your pet in their care - see our guidelines below if you have not used PetHomeStay before!"
%p.article-content
  = "Name: #{@provider.name}"
  %br
  = "Email address: #{@provider.email}"
  - if @provider.phone_number.present?
    = "Home phone: #{@provider.phone_number}"
    %br
  - if @provider.mobile_number.present?
    = "Mobile phone: #{@provider.mobile_number}"
  %br
  Listing:
  = link_to "#{@homestay.title} in #{@homestay.address_suburb}", homestay_url(@homestay)
  - if @homestay.pictures.present?
    %p.article-content= link_to image_tag(@homestay.pictures.first.file.thumb('190x150#').url), homestay_url(@homestay)
%p.article-title Next steps
%p.article-content Once you have received a couple of responses, select the provider you want to use and accept via PetHomeStay. (A provider can cancel any indicated availability up to being confirmed, so donâ€™t leave it too long!)
%p.article-content Once confirmed, both you and the provider are committed to the booking.
%p.article-content Your entire pets profile details will be sent to the Provider, including emergency contact details.
%p.article-content Any cancellations after this stage will incur the providers cancellation policy, if any, and the likelihood of negative feedback from the community!
%p= link_to "Please confirm or cancel this booking on PetHomeStay", enquiry_confirmation_url(@enquiry), class: 'btn'
%p.article-title If you have not user a provider before
%ul
  %li.article-content Be prepared to go to see the PetHomeStay or service
  %li.article-content Be upfront and honest about the type of help you expect
  %li.article-content Ensure both you and the provider have read and understand our House Rules
  %li.article-content NEVER leave your pet with, or invite into your home, someone you do not trust!
  %li.article-content Ask as many questions as you like, and remember that you do not have to accept anything whilst contacting the service provider. The only way a booking is confirmed is via your PetHomeStay notification screen.

%p.article-content Thanks and happy PetHomeStaying!
%p.article-content The PetHomeStay Team
